1
00:00:01,301 --> 00:00:03,602
I can do this...

2
00:00:03,603 --> 00:00:05,305
You can do this, Bai Xing.

3
00:00:06,272 --> 00:00:07,207
Don't be nervous.

4
00:00:07,207 --> 00:00:08,207
Just stay calm.

5
00:00:10,410 --> 00:00:12,512
You've got this.

6
00:00:14,848 --> 00:00:15,848
Here.

7
00:00:21,287 --> 00:00:22,287
Thanks.

8
00:00:25,658 --> 00:00:27,260
You were so bold a minute ago.

9
00:00:27,627 --> 00:00:29,162
Why the sudden nerves?

10
00:00:29,662 --> 00:00:31,197
I've never acted before.

11
00:00:31,498 --> 00:00:33,399
And the director just gave us lines

12
00:00:33,400 --> 00:00:34,633
without any actual plot.

13
00:00:34,634 --> 00:00:36,102
How am I supposed to play this?

14
00:00:37,737 --> 00:00:38,905
There is a plot.

15
00:00:39,572 --> 00:00:40,572
It's like this...

16
00:00:40,974 --> 00:00:42,134
I confess my feelings to you,

17
00:00:42,375 --> 00:00:44,611
and you turn me down out of insecurity.

18
00:00:45,111 --> 00:00:46,446
But then, you're moved by me.

19
00:00:48,248 --> 00:00:49,248
And then?

20
00:00:49,716 --> 00:00:50,716
Then...

21
00:00:50,750 --> 00:00:51,785
That's the end of it.

22
00:00:52,619 --> 00:00:53,253
Right.

23
00:00:53,278 --> 00:00:55,246
There are no more lines after that.

24
00:00:55,755 --> 00:00:56,423
I see.

25
00:00:56,424 --> 00:00:57,664
You're the one with experience.

26
00:00:57,724 --> 00:00:58,844
You should set the blocking.

27
00:01:04,097 --> 00:01:05,765
How are we supposed to move like this?

28
00:01:06,599 --> 00:01:07,434
You're not doing this on purpose

29
00:01:07,435 --> 00:01:08,795
just to make me look bad, are you?

30
00:01:09,936 --> 00:01:11,136
For a first-timer,

31
00:01:11,137 --> 00:01:12,439
over-planning is useless.

32
00:01:12,906 --> 00:01:14,306
Then why did you push me into this?

33
00:01:14,374 --> 00:01:15,374
Let's just go for it.

34
00:01:15,375 --> 00:01:16,409
Unless you're scared?

35
00:01:22,315 --> 00:01:23,315
Just relax.

36
00:01:24,717 --> 00:01:26,653
Do you trust me?

37
00:01:30,156 --> 00:01:31,557
Just imagine

38
00:01:31,558 --> 00:01:32,826
that I'm someone you love.

39
00:01:33,593 --> 00:01:34,794
You want to say yes,

40
00:01:35,762 --> 00:01:37,497
but you're afraid you're not good enough.

41
00:01:38,398 --> 00:01:39,398
So,

42
00:01:40,033 --> 00:01:41,601
you find an excuse to push me away.

43
00:01:42,735 --> 00:01:44,169
Not realizing

44
00:01:44,170 --> 00:01:46,004
that you're missing out on

45
00:01:46,005 --> 00:01:47,373
the best thing in your life.

46
00:01:52,512 --> 00:01:53,146
Okay.

47
00:01:53,147 --> 00:01:54,147
Just relax.

48
00:01:54,148 --> 00:01:55,482
You'll be fine.
